01:29:25.180 --> 01:29:29.180
we can be sure that our godly devotion is good.

01:29:29.180 --> 01:29:32.180
Yes, it's well maintained.

01:29:32.180 --> 01:29:39.180
So that's the first point of comparison that we'd like to make in the maintenance schedule for a vehicle

01:29:39.180 --> 01:29:42.180
