01:48:23.329 --> 01:48:29.329
So nets that are damaged or have holes in them, mending them is just like re-adjusting them.

01:48:29.329 --> 01:48:35.329
Agulation 6.1, the same verb is used of the need to re-adjust spiritually,

01:48:35.329 --> 01:48:39.329
a fellow believer who has taken a false step.

01:48:39.329 --> 01:48:47.329
The term is sometimes used in medical text to describe the setting of a barn, a limb or a joint.

01:48:47.329 --> 01:48:50.329
